13/20200114amazon08/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=January 14, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Heidi Klum]]\n* [[Tim Gunn]]\n\n===Judges===\n* [[Naomi Campbell]]\n* [[Nicole Richie]]\n* [[Chiara Ferragni]]\n* [[Carine Roitfeld]]\n* [[Joseph Altuzarra]]\n\n===Designers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Age\n! Hometown\n! Placement\n|-\n| '''Jonny Cota'''\n| '''35'''\n|''' [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], U.S.'''\n| '''Winner'''\n|-\n| Esther Perbandt\n| 43\n| [[Berlin]], Germany\n| Runner-up\n|-\n| Sander Bos\n| 24\n| [[Hasselt]], Belgium\n| 3rd\n|-\n| Megan Smith\n| 38\n| [[Kansas City, Kansas]], U.S.\n| 4th\n|-\n| Ji Won Choi\n| 26\n| [[Moore, Oklahoma]], U.S.\n| 5th\n|-\n| Rinat Brodach\n| 35\n| [[Gan Yavne]], Israel\n| 6th\n|-\n| Sabato Russo\n| 64\n| [[Milan]], Italy\n| 7th\n|-\n| Will Riddle\n| 31\n| [[Paris, Stark County, Ohio]], U.S.\n| 8th\n|-\n| Troy Arnold\n| 34\n| [[New York City]], [[New York (state)|New York]], U.S.\n| 9th\n|-\n| Joshua Hupper\n| 38\n| [[Columbus, Ohio]], U.S.\n| 10th\n|-\n| Martha Gottwald\n| 28\n| [[Richmond, Virginia]], U.S.\n| 11th\n|-\n| Jasmine Chong\n| 31\n| [[Kuala Lumpur]], Malaysia\n| 12th\n|}\n\n==Episodes==\n{{Episode table |total_width=50% |background=#0F3184 |overall= |title= |airdate= |airdateR=<ref name=\"TFC\">{{cite web |title=Making the Cut \u2013 Listings |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/making-the-cut/listings/ |website=[[The Futon Critic]] |accessdate=February 28, 2020}}</ref> |released=y |country=U.S. |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| Title           = Heidi and Tim Are Back\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|27}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n| LineColor       = 0F3184\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| Title           = Haute Couture\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|27}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n| LineColor       = 0F3184\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = Collaboration\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|4|3}}\n| ShortSummary  