Color box|limegreen|border=darkgray}} The designer won the Making The Cut Season 1.\n:{{Color box|cornflowerblue|border=darkgray}} The designer won the challenge.\n:{{Color box|turquoise|border=darkgray}} The designer had some of the best looks for the challenge but did not win.\n:{{Color box|cornsilk|border=darkgray}} The designer received feedback but was deemed safe.\n:{{Color box|white|border=darkgray}} The designer was deemed safe and did not receive feedback.\n:{{Color box|pink|border=darkgray}} The designer had some of the worst looks of the challenge but did not get eliminated.\n:{{Color box|orange|border=darkgray}} The designer was originally going to be eliminated, but the judges changed their mind.\n:{{Color box|tomato|border=darkgray||}} The designer was eliminated from the competition.\n\n==Production==\nOn September 7, 2018, it was announced that Klum and Gunn would be leaving ''[[Project Runway]]'' to develop a fashion [[reality television]] series for [[Prime Video]].<ref name=\"deadline-09-18\">{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Heidi Klum & Tim Gunn Exit \u2018Project Runway\u2019, Team With Amazon For New Fashion Reality Series|url=https://deadline.com/2018/09/heidi-klum-tim-gunn-exit-project-runway-amazon-new-fashion-reality-series-1202459089/|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=September 7, 2018|accessdate=September 7, 2018}}</ref>\n\nOn June 26, 2019, it was announced that the series would be called ''Making the Cut'' and that Campbell, Richie, Roitfeld and Altuzarra would be judges on the show.<ref name=\"deadline-06-19\">{{cite web|last=Petski|first=Denise|title=Heidi Klum & Tim Gunn\u2019s Amazon Fashion Competition Series Gets Title, Naomi Campbell & Nicole Richie Among Judges|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/heidi-klum-tim-gunn-amazon-fashion-competition-series-title-naomi-campbell-nicole-richie-judges-1202638127|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=June 26, 2019|accessdate=June 26, 2019|language=en}}</ref><ref name=\"hollywood-reporter-06-19\">{{cite web|last=Real|first=Evan|title=Amazon Unveils Judges, Title of Heidi Klum and Tim Gunn's Fashion Competition Series|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/making-cut-first-look-at-heidi-klum-tim-gunns-amazon-fashion-series-1221054|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=June 26, 2019|accessdate=June 26, 2019|language=en}}</ref>\n\nThe series is executive produced by Klum, Gunn, Sara Rea, Page Feldman and Jennifer Love through SKR Productions.<ref name=\"deadline-06-19\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.amazon.com/makingthecut ''Making the Cut''] on [[Prime Video]]\n* {{IMDb title|8962394}}\n\n{{Amazon Video original series}}\n\n[[Category:2020 American television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2020s American reality television series]]\n[[Category:Amazon Video original programming]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Television series by Amazon Studios]]\n", "name_user": "98.116.6.23", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eCast:I\u2019ve added the highly requested model Adreena Thompson.)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Making_the_Cut_(2020_TV_series)"}
